==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: groundbreaking
<hw>ground"break`ing</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <def>The ceremonial breaking of
the ground to formally begin a construction project. It is sometimes
carried out by an official who digs the first spadeful of dirt from the
ground, to begin the preparatory excavation work.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> groundbreaking ceremony.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

